<concept id="concept_1BCF5C425D7D4627AB1C66A085CF6E11"
            xml:lang="en-us">
    <title>Preparing the Installation Directory</title>
    <conbody>
        <section>
            <p>On the Docker host, you need to create a directory which holds various data, such as persistent database data or configuration data. In this document, this directory is referred to as <codeph>/docker</codeph>:</p>
            <p>On the Docker host, execute the following command: </p>
            <p>
                <codeblock>mkdir /docker</codeblock>
            </p>
        </section>
    </conbody>
</concept>
